{"questionId":"3514788","questionHtml":"<p>Calculate the volume of ice cream that is not inside the cone.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>Multiplying their volume by <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> (M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(A1</strong><strong>)</strong></em></p>\n<p>Subtracting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></math> of their volume&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> The <em><strong>M1</strong></em> can be awarded for a final answer of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>32</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9272</mn><mo>…</mo></math> seen without working.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>132</mn><mo> </mo><msup><mi>cm</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>131</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>708</mn><mo>…</mo><mo> </mo><msup><mi>cm</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3514788","referenceCode":"23M.1.SL.TZ2.8a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Calculate the volume of ice cream that is not inside the cone.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","SL 3.1—3d space, volume, angles, midpoints"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}